@startuml alanchn31_Movalytics-Data-Warehouse
skinparam rectangle {
  BackgroundColor #ffffff
  BorderColor black
  Style roundrect
}
left to right direction

rectangle "Kaggle API" as Kaggle
rectangle "FRED API" as FRED
rectangle "S3 Bucket" as S3
rectangle "Apache Airflow" as Airflow {
  rectangle "DAG Scheduler" as Scheduler
  rectangle "Web Server" as Webserver
}
rectangle "Apache Spark" as Spark
rectangle "Amazon Redshift" as Redshift

' ========== Data Flow ==========
Kaggle --> S3 : MovieLens dataset (CSV)
FRED --> S3 : CPI data (CSV)

Airflow --> S3 : Trigger ETL pipeline
S3 --> Spark : Read raw data
Spark --> Redshift : Write to staging tables
Redshift --> Redshift : Upsert to dimension tables

' ========== Control Flow ==========
Webserver --> Scheduler : Submit DAG
Scheduler --> Spark : Execute Spark jobs
Spark --> Scheduler : Job completion status
Scheduler --> Redshift : Run data quality checks
Redshift --> Scheduler : Data quality results

' ========== Internal Airflow ==========
Webserver -right-> Scheduler : Monitor DAG runs
@enduml